Description.en:
Perform a quick Dodge Roll.
Can be used to instantly break out of animation locks.
<yellow>{Press-hold to start sprinting after a roll.}

Description.zh:
快速进行闪避翻滚。
可以立即解除动画锁定状态。
<yellow>{长按以在翻滚后开始奔跑。}

Description.en:
Allows contextual interaction within the environment.
<yellow>{- Can be bound on the same Bind Slot as other Skills
- Can only be associated to one Bind Slot at a time}

Description.zh:
可以与环境进行情境互动。
<yellow>{可以与其他技能绑定在同一个绑定栏中。
同一时间只能分配给一个绑定栏。}
